self.assertEqual(u'[g,f]-colorings of Partial k-trees', latex_to_unicode(
    '$[g,f]$-colorings of Partial $k$-trees', capitalize='title'))
self.assertEqual(u'On K_3,3-free or K_5-free Graphs', latex_to_unicode(
    'On {$K_{3,3}$}-free or {$K_5$}-free graphs', capitalize='title'))
self.assertEqual(u'Clique-width ≤3 Graphs', latex_to_unicode(
    'clique-width $\\leq 3$ graphs', capitalize='title'))
self.assertEqual(u'An O(n^2.5) Algorithm', latex_to_unicode(
    'An {O}($n^{2.5}$) Algorithm', capitalize='title'))
self.assertEqual(u'An n × N Board', latex_to_unicode(
    'an $n \\times n$ board', capitalize='title'))
self.assertEqual(u'Of k-trees Is O(k)', latex_to_unicode(
    'of \\mbox{$k$-trees} is {$O(k)$}', capitalize='title'))
